## Limitations
This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of studies reviewed. Some articles did not specify publication dates, which may affect the timeliness of the information. Additionally, while the report highlights the correlation between loneliness and mental health issues, it does not explore causation in depth. Further research is needed to understand the underlying mechanisms and to develop effective interventions.